Comment: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從這世界上...
Comment: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了嗎? 艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,徹底地殺光
Comment: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從這世上...
Comment: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一隻不留地...
Comment: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這一年中央政府決定
Comment: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將人類的活動領域
Comment: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,後退到羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這之中被巨人吃掉的人數
Comment: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大約有一萬人
Comment: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:59.14,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卡露拉
Comment: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我平安無事啊
Comment: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸 住手 爸爸
Comment: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想要幹嘛?
Comment: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點給我把手臂伸出來
Comment: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.62,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要！
Comment: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸因為媽媽死了就變得很奇怪
Comment: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放開我 爸爸
Comment: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是...為了你
Comment: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什麼
Comment: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別忘記鑰匙
Comment: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總有一天...
Comment: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,...直到那一天
Comment: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧
Comment: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,做惡夢了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,感覺似乎見到了爸爸
Comment: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼可能...那是夢
Comment: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是這樣嗎...
Comment: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧
Comment: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽說有發放食物
Comment: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽說這裡是食物倉庫
Comment: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,坐船來的人通通被聚集在這裡
Comment: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這邊也是
Comment: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好好排隊
Comment: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了 我可是從昨天晚上就什麼都沒吃
Comment: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們並非是真的活下來了
Comment: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你看 我趕上了
Comment: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,叔叔說這是小孩子的份 特別給我們的
Comment: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝
Comment: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他是怎樣啊
Comment: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也是沒辦法的
Comment: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個補給應該不夠分給所有人
Comment: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣就是一天份
Comment: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難民太多了
Comment: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且原本食物就不足了
Comment: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你也知道住在外層的人都不被重視
Comment: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為何要為了外人用我們的補給
Comment: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正巨人都破壞掉城牆進來了
Comment: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果能吃掉更多人就好了
Comment: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣只會讓食物不足更嚴重
Comment: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好痛
Comment: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼...
Comment: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在做什麼 死小鬼
Comment: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明什麼都不知道
Comment: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你明明什麼都沒看過!
Comment: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人...
Comment: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是怎麼將人給...
Comment: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了!
Comment: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對不起 !
Comment: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他因為肚子餓 有點火大
Comment: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以才會對大人們做這樣不禮貌的事情
Comment: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的... 很抱歉!
Comment: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是的...
Comment: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們之所以不用挨餓
Comment: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是託我們的福啊
Comment: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是小孩 好歹也給我懷點感謝的心
Comment: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好
Comment: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡
Comment: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰要受那樣的人的照顧
Comment: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回去給你看 回到原來的瑪利亞之牆...
Comment: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把巨人給全部殺光
Comment: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不是認真的吧?
Comment: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是認真的!
Comment: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟那些在城牆裡逞強的人不同
Comment: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種東西我才不需要!
Comment: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會餓死的喔!
Comment: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你難道不會不甘心嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是一直受到這樣的恩惠 才會打不贏巨人
Comment: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不可能啦 怎麼可能打得贏
Comment: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們只能活在城牆裡面
Comment: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亂來的話就會死
Comment: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就像我的爸媽一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我們就要向他們嘻皮笑臉嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不會感到羞恥嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在... 現在也是沒辦法的啊!
Comment: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「沒辦法」什麼的 我聽膩了!
Comment: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那你就繼續這樣像個家畜一樣活著吧 膽小鬼!!
Comment: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎...
Comment: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏是膽小鬼的話...
Comment: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連跟我也是一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們無論是從巨人手上逃走 還是逃離城鎮
Comment: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說到底我們什麼都沒做
Comment: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今天的食物也是別人給的
Comment: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣沒有力量的人類...
Comment: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要打倒一隻巨人都不可能
Comment: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最重要的是活下去
Comment: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就跟阿姨說的一樣
Comment: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎...
Comment: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我吃掉...
Comment: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好好地活下去
Comment: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不會讓艾連餓死的
Comment: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,數日後大量的難民
Comment: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了確保食物
Comment: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,負責荒地的開墾
Comment: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 食物不足的災難並沒有結束
Comment: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隔年的846年 中央政府以奪回瑪利亞之牆的名義
Comment: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將大量的難民投入於戰爭上
Comment: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總數約二十五萬人...
Comment: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,相當於人口的兩成
Comment: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但生存下來的僅100多人...
Comment: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這些犧牲讓活下來的人類的食物不足
Comment: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,逐漸獲得改善
Comment: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全部都是巨人的錯...
Comment: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要將他們打倒
Comment: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就連我們的歸宿也能夠奪回
Comment: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我明年會志願加入訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了得到打倒巨人的力量
Comment: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也...
Comment: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也要...
Comment: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也去
Comment: 0,0:20:58.79,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳不去沒有關係
Comment: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳不是說最重要的是活下去嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯...
Comment: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我是為了不讓你死而去
Comment: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我知道了...
Comment: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,三人一起...
Comment: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Comment: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在起第104期訓練軍團入團儀式正式開始
Comment: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是很衰小負責帶領你們的吉斯．夏提斯
Comment: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒有歡迎你們的意思!
Comment: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以現在的你們來說
Comment: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只不過是給巨人當作食物的家畜
Comment: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是比家畜更卑微的存在
Comment: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於你們這種什麼都辦不到的傢伙
Comment: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們會花三年的時間來訓練你們
Comment: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,徹底灌輸好你們打倒巨人的技術
Comment: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,三年後 你們站在巨人面前時
Comment: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是飼料而已呢?
Comment: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是保護國王的名譽之牆呢?
Comment: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或是消滅巨人的光榮士兵呢?
Comment: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,由你們自己來決定吧!!
Comment: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會成為的...
Comment: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將巨人一隻不剩地趕盡殺絕
Comment: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Comment: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作為士兵失格
Comment: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發誓要對巨人復仇
Comment: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成為了訓練兵的艾連
Comment: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在基礎訓練的失敗中 所直視的真實面貌
Comment: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是非常殘酷的
