Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}距今100年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出現了人類的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們與人類之間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有著壓倒性的力量之差
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類差點就陷入了絕種的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}倖存下來的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}建造了瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}三座城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}實現了100年的平安生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到彼時到來前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吾毫無幸福可言 靈魂早已墜入慾望深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}此刻誠如汝所見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吾將為此遭受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}貪婪下的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吾等只能悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}獻食吾等生靈之罪孽制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在吾所在的這山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再無彼此更痛苦的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放開我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊! 貪欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}汝將吾等血族拉至汝身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吾等以己之肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}若再不反省回顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又能有何作為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}貪欲啊 乳膠吾等血族拉至汝...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明差一點就能救到媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要給我多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}差一點點..就能將媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.37,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我適可而止點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你之所以沒有辦法救出你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為你沒有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我之所以沒辦法面對巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為我沒有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊...又變成這樣了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點 往裡面疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用停靠在那邊的船逃離希干希納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點 不然要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}位於城牆外側
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟希干希納區一樣突出的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做為吸引巨人的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}達成了降低警備成本與兵力的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如同它的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做為巨人們的目標的希干希納居民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只好從唯一的一個後門逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部人都給我把行李丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能多讓一個人上去也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是艾連跟米卡莎還沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在先別說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看那個樣子想必...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在磨蹭些什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}砲彈怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神明大人..神明大人..神明大人..神明大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5} 已經客滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼這樣 拜託讓我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使只有小孩子也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很抱歉 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}混帳 在瞄準哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是這東西沒有瞄準器可以瞄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在那種事情隨便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點裝填下一枚砲彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}門要關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撤退 要被關在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別關門 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有很多人留在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果這扇門被突破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這可不是一座城市被占據就能了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類的活動區域 將被迫退到下一座城牆後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算如此也沒有理由對自己眼前的人見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點關起來 巨人要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點關門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開火!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了 撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}衝過來了 快點將門...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}門被...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞之牆南部希干希納區淪陷數小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這件事情傳遍了人類領域內的各個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是真的嗎? 希干希納被巨人入侵了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撐了100年的城牆為何現在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論你相不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在可是真的有坐船逃出的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依照報告有500人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}問題是只有希干希納而已嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 應該不可能侵入到瑪利亞之牆的內陸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之先通知中央 等待指示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種緊急狀況 光憑我們無法作出對策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就在剛剛快馬來報 瑪利亞之牆被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}內陸被巨人入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類又要被巨人吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結束...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經無法...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回到那個家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到最後我還在跟她做無謂的鬥嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哪裡都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為...你沒有力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是我..因為人類太弱小了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道弱者就只能哭泣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把他們...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世界上...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了嗎? 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}徹底地殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世上...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這一年中央政府決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將人類的活動領域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後退到羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這之中被巨人吃掉的人數
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大約有一萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸 住手 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想要幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點給我把手臂伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.62,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸因為媽媽死了就變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放開我 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別忘記鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總有一天...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}...直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做惡夢了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}感覺似乎見到了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼可能...那是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是這樣嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽說有發放食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽說這裡是食物倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}坐船來的人通通被聚集在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好好排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了 我可是從昨天晚上就什麼都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們並非是真的活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你看 我趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}叔叔說這是小孩子的份 特別給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個補給應該不夠分給所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣就是一天份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難民太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且原本食物就不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你也知道住在外層的人都不被重視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為何要為了外人用我們的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正巨人都破壞掉城牆進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果能吃掉更多人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣只會讓食物不足更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在做什麼 死小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你明明什麼都沒看過!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是怎麼將人給...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起 !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他因為肚子餓 有點火大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以才會對大人們做這樣不禮貌的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真的... 很抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們之所以不用挨餓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是託我們的福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是小孩 好歹也給我懷點感謝的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰要受那樣的人的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回去給你看 回到原來的瑪利亞之牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把巨人給全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不是認真的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是認真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟那些在城牆裡逞強的人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種東西我才不需要!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會餓死的喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你難道不會不甘心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是一直受到這樣的恩惠 才會打不贏巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可能啦 怎麼可能打得贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們只能活在城牆裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亂來的話就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就像我的爸媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我們就要向他們嘻皮笑臉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不會感到羞恥嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在... 現在也是沒辦法的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「沒辦法」什麼的 我聽膩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那你就繼續這樣像個家畜一樣活著吧 膽小鬼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏是膽小鬼的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連跟我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們無論是從巨人手上逃走 還是逃離城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說到底我們什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}今天的食物也是別人給的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣沒有力量的人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要打倒一隻巨人都不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最重要的是活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就跟阿姨說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我吃掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好好地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會讓艾連餓死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}數日後大量的難民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了確保食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.75,Default,Q,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}負責荒地的開墾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 食物不足的災難並沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隔年的846年 中央政府以奪回瑪利亞之牆的名義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將大量的難民投入於戰爭上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總數約二十五萬人...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相當於人口的兩成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但生存下來的僅100多人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這些犧牲讓活下來的人類的食物不足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}逐漸獲得改善
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部都是巨人的錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要將他們打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連我們的歸宿也能夠奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我明年會志願加入訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了得到打倒巨人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳不去沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳不是說最重要的是活下去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我是為了不讓你死而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我知道了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}三人一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在起第104期訓練軍團入團儀式正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是很衰小負責帶領你們的吉斯．夏提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有歡迎你們的意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以現在的你們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只不過是給巨人當作食物的家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是比家畜更卑微的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對於你們這種什麼都辦不到的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們會花三年的時間來訓練你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}徹底灌輸好你們打倒巨人的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}三年後 你們站在巨人面前時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是飼料而已呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是保護國王的名譽之牆呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或是消滅巨人的光榮士兵呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}由你們自己來決定吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會成為的...
